# Python project template

## Usage

```sh
pip install rapidrush
cd /move/to/your/project/directory
rapid-start
```

or

```sh
git clone https://github.com/bluelief/rapidrush.git
cd rapidrush
python setup.py install
cd /move/to/your/project/directory
rapid-start
```
